{
  "stem": "802.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[POLISH] And I played the lead role, and my sister played also an important role.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were two Jewish actors who never identified as Jews, but they were catapulted into the ghetto anyway.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Michal, Michael, Michal Znicz, and Irena, which is a woman, Irena Brezka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were the ones who guided us, who taught us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they promised me and my mother that, if we survived the war, they'll train me, because I was so gifted.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, they told it to everyone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every child was told that he or she was gifted, and they'll train them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I found out about it later through, you know, sort of-- not directly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I'm sure they did it anyway, because the troupe kept our morale up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, all of these things were extremely important.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So initially, the conditions were not as bad, but they became progressively worse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You may know that, until 1942, the Germans did not intend to gas the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is to say, they were not-- they did not intend to send them into the gas chambers-- in Majdanek, where I was, Auschwitz, Sobibor, Treblinka, and the others-- but, ultimately, this was their decision.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And things became just absolutely awful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But even in the beginning, they would round up people-- the Germans, Lithuanians were notorious.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Lithuanians were extremely cruel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Really, they were bestial.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Lithuanians, Ukrainians, used round up people-- pick people up from the street, put them onto a truck and send them off.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the irony and the tragedy of it is that these people were made to write letters to us from wherever they, they said they were sent east, and everything is fine.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
